title: Catalan Independence | Why?
description:
Following last Sunday's independence referendum in Catalonia, I've made a video to try and explain why the region wants to break away from the rest of Spain.

Note:
I am aware that Franco repressed all of Spain and not just Catalonia - I feel that this particular topic would require another video for discussion. I know that other regions and anyone associated with the Republic suffered. 

Don't forget to subscribe -  youtube.com/user/JustMattWatson

TWITTER - twitter.com/JustMattWatson
INSTAGRAM - instagram.com/justmattwatson
TUMBLR - justmattwatson.tumblr.com/

Enquiries: justmattwatson@outlook.com

"Just Matt Watson", written and performed by Joe Ragosta. Permission granted for use on social media.
